message.text: I stopped in Ace Florist in Syosset last week to order a bouquet for a co-worker who was retiring.  I cannot tell you how many compliments were received by the stunning arrangement! Long after the flowers were taken home, the sweet sent was still filling the office.  Thank you Pat for creating such a beautiful arrangement!
